hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722eca77fbf59dd706026f22c7b625f4e982f626","tid":1365461,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"!!!一站式 分門別類 公務員 公營機構 開花 Facebook Page!!! 已開：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=bd0e6f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 分好晒唔同部門，睇睇同事諗緊乜<br />\n2. 集中一個地方，唔同部門間互相打氣，唔使只係自己友圍爐<br />\n3. 綜合唔同平台嘅post, 令力量更大<br />\n4. 不停更新，唔怕post沈底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去呢個Page,可以透過以下方法：<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Form : <a href=\"https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ/exec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscript.google.com%2Fmacros%2Fs%2FAKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ%2Fexec&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=7e66d88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx3iXYrOgGQhE1ESqUjWtdNXXVJk6L6gVVaaY-qF8xwdGtPbYTZ/exec</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook msg: @civilservantsflowers<br />\n<br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=9ee4d13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人手勁唔夠，如果有錯有漏麻煩屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\n感激各位冇TLDR